name: Teeth Trouble: The Stakeholding Encroachment
description:
Now in fullscreen.

Make sure Mr. Stakeholder is pleased!

Made for the 2023 Global Game Jam.

To my outstanding roommates I say --

Many thanks to the wonderful Justin Michael Cook for modeling the majority of the 3D assets, and for his incredible help in developing sound for the game! To my other roommate, Alexanger, I give thanks for the coding advice! And my final roommate Jeffaray, although no assistance from you was received, I recognize the nobility in your assistive intentions, and know how much better this game would have been were it not for the unfortunate timing of my asking for your help  in musical composition, sensei.
